{"tid":1031180,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"心血來潮想整個beef Wellington(第一次整 手下留情）","createTime":"2019-02-21T12:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T04:49:32.000Z","uid":147271,"like":82,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d1642045a30b97a42013c0a6215b4326220bbbd7","tid":1031180,"uid":147271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:54:49.000Z","msg":"細佬今日心血來潮想食beef Wellington 所以就買料整啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次整beef Wellington 好多敗筆 請大家手下留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日去aeon買咗呢堆野 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uhuEsMn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuhuEsMn.png&h=fe2b43d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住就返屋企開始整啦 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CbDJUr9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCbDJUr9.png&h=673c2214&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dd8JUr9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDd8JUr9.png&h=83549b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘑菇切到勁細變泥 其實應該用打碎機打碎佢 但屋企冇只好慢慢切 結果切咗成10-15min<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9p9w3kv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9p9w3kv.png&h=fe038e06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M8BCYTS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM8BCYTS.png&h=a1fe1a72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟手set好啲火腿for第一次卷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mssuP07.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmssuP07.png&h=d0b6e2b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟手就先煎一煎個牛柳嘅表皮 封死啲肉汁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XY4pDUT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXY4pDUT.png&h=259b55a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uBUMSeV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuBUMSeV.png&h=f5a43f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uEALzW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uEALzW.png&h=8b969ad0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rff0WGC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRff0WGC.png&h=e97c0270&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ZCq7Oi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ZCq7Oi.png&h=22875051&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uV4tk8j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuV4tk8j.png&h=4b918476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住就拎出黎放一下 比佢休息下 而一拎出黎就要放芥末 等佢係休息嘅時候吸收入去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gptt5Aj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGptt5Aj.png&h=d90ce4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住就將啲蘑菇泥炒到出曬水 再炒乾佢 等佢冇曬水份<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GbKALAr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbKALAr.png&h=97d53db4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qoPALAs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqoPALAs.png&h=32cd1ba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後就第一次裝卷佢啦<br />\n用保鮮紙卷到佢好似日式啲飯卷咁 再係兩邊頭尾扭實定佢個形 再放佢落雪櫃5-10min 等佢定形 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0t82qAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0t82qAW.png&h=141a5f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4CBrSfX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4CBrSfX.png&h=1b916547&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pim7BHD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPim7BHD.png&h=63302e01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等佢定形之後就拎出黎再做多次上面嘅步驟 但將火腿換成酥皮（其實成件事比酥皮禍咗成件事 最後再講）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cCSOk9T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcCSOk9T.png&h=ac74fab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等5-10min佢定形之後就拎出黎 打蛋黃搽喺表面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91OBu3Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91OBu3Q.png&h=a5cffaa4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPT57Qw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPT57Qw.png&h=add2fc97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再拎去220度焗25min<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1U5opm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1U5opm.png&h=4b41eb47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拎出黎了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9DNq7Re.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9DNq7Re.png&h=f8e94bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n切開 生熟就岩岩好 但其實地方出咗事 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FLnOmbp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFLnOmbp.png&h=c860cd9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ww8mGbq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWw8mGbq.png&h=4a0e1877&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OdWn94M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOdWn94M.png&h=eea6aea4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tW0ch6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tW0ch6.png&h=9af731bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MSNyxh7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMSNyxh7.png&h=bb30d4ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食落嘅感覺係幾唔錯 而且好軟好lum 同時都好多汁 夠味 <br />\n但敗筆位開始黎啦<br />\n1.買錯酥皮 因為岩岩去aeon買果啲佢得一種酥皮 而我冇買過酥皮 所以就唔理咁多 同時附近都冇其他超市揀 所以就局住買 但點知買完就出事 佢唔係一層厚小小嘅皮 而係一大堆好薄嘅皮 於是我就用咗三分一一野包落去 點知就出事 第一太厚 第二太多層個質感唔岩 而禍咗beef Wellington 脆口表皮嘅特色<br />\n2.蘑菇同芥末啲量唔多 味係有係到 但可以多返啲個口感會豐富啲 <br />\n3.搽蛋黃果時重手咗 <br />\n呢三個係大家整果時可以留意嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整體黎講我覺得不錯係幾好食 特別係個肉 只係個表皮壞咗啲 細佬第一次整beef Wellington 希望大家手下留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92547248974a095f2ab1313fe438a8996f75af47","tid":1031180,"uid":147271,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:58:08.000Z","msg":"同時時整咗個豬扒食下咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/svuUgOS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsvuUgOS.png&h=f8852979&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a97fc95d974baa3d6938682f619ab6e56476354","tid":1031180,"uid":78971,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"92547248974a095f2ab1313fe438a8996f75af47","tid":1031180,"uid":147271,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:58:08.000Z","msg":"同時時整咗個豬扒食下咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/svuUgOS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsvuUgOS.png&h=f8852979&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:00:06.000Z","msg":"仲吸引過上面舊牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3bad3c42a65a96ab4e17efaaa3778eaa46089bc","tid":1031180,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89349bffae36a268f85400292468003e04228199","tid":1031180,"uid":147271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a97fc95d974baa3d6938682f619ab6e56476354","tid":1031180,"uid":78971,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"92547248974a095f2ab1313fe438a8996f75af47","tid":1031180,"uid":147271,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:58:08.000Z","msg":"同時時整咗個豬扒食下咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/svuUgOS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsvuUgOS.png&h=f8852979&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:00:06.000Z","msg":"仲吸引過上面舊牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:00:48.000Z","msg":"舊牛第一次整🙁"},{"pid":"4c2ba089858ab32a6446021d10f1b48f4d1c2110","tid":1031180,"uid":196968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:01:58.000Z","msg":"嘩好撚正咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7038aba567921803fb59ba2b77880678640b2524","tid":1031180,"uid":191572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:03:58.000Z","msg":"食好多肉🥴"},{"pid":"652f804b125c9ab32e37d3d13603adb4e8516e2f","tid":1031180,"uid":186818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"整牛嘅post 竟然正皮多過負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a607a6a96b5246d6b02b2dd2ca5d662c0ead9d3","tid":1031180,"uid":138155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"652f804b125c9ab32e37d3d13603adb4e8516e2f","tid":1031180,"uid":186818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"整牛嘅post 竟然正皮多過負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T18:14:06.000Z","msg":"因為同某個成日整牛嘅會員 對比起上嚟好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b638db4f6ed02b7e0207722114b73e193b17ae1","tid":1031180,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:13:03.000Z","msg":"個豬鞍扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e55a62b32e767fe2efaf9665bc6d6ebae67e1f7","tid":1031180,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似好好食咁，邊有失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d233a1cd387694da4163f6bc1c98c2900bea0128","tid":1031180,"uid":14349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T00:25:53.000Z","msg":"第一次整係咁㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n比d心機下次會好好多"},{"pid":"571d1918b6eded8c0c49c71a4fab0190827c86ca","tid":1031180,"uid":60860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:26:08.000Z","msg":"想睇整豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會講埋"},{"pid":"1172d6a3bb242727c875f3d24f0510bb42f69606","tid":1031180,"uid":162906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:33:26.000Z","msg":"好正."},{"pid":"90c37696f70b866f971dc984723eed835b4f416c","tid":1031180,"uid":194671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:06:53.000Z","msg":"搽蛋黃重手左會點？<br />\n係咪會易燶啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a33cf317b9118079b8c44f1cda5a6a9f6935e32","tid":1031180,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:37:57.000Z","msg":"酥皮界紋會靚仔啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好正㗎啦"},{"pid":"53d18e7f062efb087a04a85c0346db54f30d2f2c","tid":1031180,"uid":147271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"571d1918b6eded8c0c49c71a4fab0190827c86ca","tid":1031180,"uid":60860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:26:08.000Z","msg":"想睇整豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會講埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:46:22.000Z","msg":"下次搵日開po講 但其實都只係就咁煎香兩邊再煎到佢熟就係了 個汁我做咁一個英式芥末 就落咗啲牛油煮一煮 同埋另一個係黑醋汁 就咁放咗係邊自己點<br />\n只係影咗一張相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HuVXjRF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHuVXjRF.png&h=99b06f38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7fca000805b9c7e4f98581cb0cdaeff5c6b16ed3","tid":1031180,"uid":147271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90c37696f70b866f971dc984723eed835b4f416c","tid":1031180,"uid":194671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T02:06:53.000Z","msg":"搽蛋黃重手左會點？<br />\n係咪會易燶啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:47:01.000Z","msg":"個表皮嘅色會冇咁靚"},{"pid":"2c71cdfa19d624ae418ccf1afaa88d4f204fa802","tid":1031180,"uid":147271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a33cf317b9118079b8c44f1cda5a6a9f6935e32","tid":1031180,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:37:57.000Z","msg":"酥皮界紋會靚仔啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好正㗎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"我本身有打算！但結果果個我啲酥皮係一張張好薄嘅皮所以做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406ca0dff8bd25c4ea97f9f177a2fb7cde89a18f","tid":1031180,"uid":2667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T04:49:32.000Z","msg":"用錯部位喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}